%D A046902 J. E. Clark, Clark's triangle, Math. Student, 26 (No. 2, 1978), p. 4.
%H A046902 Harvey P. Dale, <a href="/A046902/b046902.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000</a>
